{"type": "article", "id": 41702, "title": "想缓解焦虑？试试这个无限魔方｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-06-06T23:01:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33067, "name": "Tough Slate Design"}, {"id": 41193, "name": "Bastion"}, {"id": 41194, "name": "Engineerable"}, {"id": 41195, "name": "Craig & Karl"}, {"id": 41196, "name": "Samurai Age"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 189, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170606211627atGsUZ9Vq8IPFSHl.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Infinity Cube by Bastion &amp; Engineerable</h3><p>减压玩具也可以做得简洁又好看。美国日用配件品牌 <a href=\"http://www.magplates.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bastion</a> 和设计工作室 <a href=\"http://engineerable.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Engineerable</a> 近日联手推出了这款看起来相当低调的铝制魔方 Infinity Cube，它由八个可以从任意角度旋转的立方体构成，在玩法上不作任何限制。虽然看起来四四方方很难携带，只要折叠成 2 厘米厚的平面状态就可以轻松地放进口袋里了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1270603883/fidget-in-style-with-infinity-cube-luxury-edc-fidg\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 75 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211655WExXKNDrSahGcstF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211656RFjM73mHS2BxbYiN.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211655nQYNEM4Tlcm1ZKkR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211655gOojVlIuQPRCU3kD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211656ZqaW5wB0JXG3REur.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bouncy Layers by nendo</h3><p>要让家居变得舒适柔软，不一定只有通过泡沫、棉花和弹簧才能达成。在第二届家居概念设计展“家生活 创无界”上，日本设计工作室 nendo 采用 1.5 毫米厚的聚碳酸酯板取代了家具中常见的靠垫，推出了这套让柔软这一概念变得可见的家具系列 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/bouncy-layers/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bouncy Layers</a>。这种板材的柔软度会根据两层之间的空间大小发生变化，因此可以创造出满足不同功能、软硬兼备的弹性层。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211717NX20kU48LiaYFbpA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211717MYxFQa9DkblB3PfS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211717aPGXeZqrw7Q49T2O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211718Ig8DFK0QXn6lVodZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211717tCFuoWbeZM12dgQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211717stou9ckQDpgU6Lvy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>CROQUIS by QUPA</h3><p>QUPA 是一个由希腊建筑师 Eleni Kouineli 和 Stefanos Papadatos 共同创立的设计工作室，最近他们将自己热爱的手工艺与专业结合，推出了一个以建筑平面图为原型的首饰品牌 CROQUIS。希腊众多的名胜古迹为他们提供了丰富的创作素材，包括雅典卫城博物馆、万神庙和圣乔治圆厅在内的建筑都被制作成了项链或是耳环。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/QUPA\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价从 47.74 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706062117354siWvQer3kgMdX1u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211735gTdQx9rmqhkAVZL6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.127500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211735P2ubtwpL5UIVnJD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211736GQ0l6DjIUnqmho1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.357500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Samurai Armor by Samurai Age</h3><p>来自日本的 <a href=\"https://www.samurai-age.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Samurai Age</a> 是一个致力于开发轻量版武士铠甲的设计公司，除了服饰之外，还推出过酒瓶专用的铠甲保护套。最近，他们又推出了一条针对宠物的产品线，让喵星人和汪星人也能像人类一样 cosplay 一把诸如真田幸村这样的日本战国英雄。这是铠甲的<a href=\"https://www.samurai-age.jp/shop/products/list.php?category_id=8\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 14040 日元起，头盔则需要额外定制。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211753jcWMXZEkdb4liC06.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211753n54H2mTbs9GMUWjS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211754xawnL1qlyWCN2ez0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211753QhrbUkeCm7cLq90l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jola by Tough Slate Design</h3><p>为了吸引年轻的消费者，一家来自乌克兰的公司推出了将蜂蜜、香料和果汁混合在一起的蜂蜜混合物，并委托 Tough Slate Design 工作室操刀<a href=\"http://toughslatedesign.com/jola-honey-mix\" rel=\"nofollow\">形象设计</a>。设计团队根据乌克兰语中蜂蜜一词的发音，衍生出了便于记忆的品牌名 JOLA。类似水油混合的图案不仅巧妙地点明了每款混合物所使用的原料，也暗示了产品不同于普通蜂蜜的质感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211821gWkTX4NP0z1KUbCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211822bfnxQycqAG0DRUFW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706062118218rBudL9ex5gXOcwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211822JeFTjznaI0XKfNm2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211821NfyPG7cp05dVMtbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Here After by Craig &amp; Karl</h3><p>如果你最近前往伦敦北侧的白城区（White City），不妨去看看这个经艺术家组合 <a href=\"http://www.craigandkarl.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Craig &amp; Karl</a> 之手而焕然一新的 pop-up 活动场地 Here After。为了向白城区悠久的广播历史致敬（这里曾经是 BBC 总部的所在地），他们在这座废弃的加油站内绘制了一系列让人联想到电视测试卡的图案，相当吸睛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211900WlAixnyBRjbr03Eu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.753056\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170606211900l6mQnad21oTX7Z4H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}